1. Musk changed the account name to Kekius Maximus at night;
2. Galaxy Digital officially listed on Nasdaq with the stock code GLXY;
3. WLFI USD1 stablecoin integrates Chainlink CCIP to achieve multi-chain availability;
4. Argentine judge ordered the freezing of assets of key figures in the LIBRA project, including reviewing the financial transactions of President Milley and his sister;
5. The 5x short HYPE whale suffered a floating loss of US$12.06 million and withdrew 3 million USDC from Binance as margin again;
6. The 25x short ETH address has a floating profit of US$2.4 million, which was dormant for 4 years;
7. The suspected team address transferred 6.7 million LDO to CEX in the past 20 hours, and 17.81 million LDO to CEX in the past 4 days;
8. Ethereum spot ETF had a total net inflow of US$22.117 million yesterday, and none of the nine ETFs had a net outflow;
9. Bitcoin spot ETF had a total net inflow of 2.60 yesterday US$100 million, a net inflow for 3 consecutive days;
10. Huang Licheng once again added 36,759 HYPEs.
